g%20on%20a%20laptop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F633730ea94aa2f0018cfcd1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22992%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnline%20tutoring%20is%20a%20side%20hustle%20that%20can%20help%20you%20build%20communication%20skills.%3Cp%3Ejose%20carlos%20cerdeno%20martinez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20I%20was%20still%20working%20full-time%2C%20my%20companies%20never%20offered%20professional%20development.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESo%20I%20took%20on%20side%20hustles%20to%20learn%20new%20skills%20like%20marketing%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20writing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20recommend%20freelancing%2C%20running%20an%20e-commerce%20business%2C%20and%20tutoring%20to%20help%20you%20earn%20more%20at%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20was%20a%20full-time%20entrepreneur%2C%20I%20worked%20for%20startups%20and%20big%20companies%2C%20always%20eager%20for%20a%20promotion%20or%20raise.%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20on%20more%20responsibilities%2C%20new%20job%20titles%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20a%20higher%20salary%20that%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20meet%20more%20of%20my%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20saw%20that%20my%20employers%20weren't%20offering%20or%20funding%20any%20professional%20development%20programs%20that%20would%20help%20me%20advance%2C%20though%2C%20I%20took%20my%20development%20into%20my%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20start%20pursuing%20side%20hustles%20that%20would%20help%20me%20improve%20or%20learn%20new%20skills%20and%20also%20get%20paid%20in%20the%20meantime.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20these%20after-work%20gigs%2C%20I%20showed%20my%20boss%20an%20updated%20portfolio%20of%20what%20I%20had%20been%20working%20on%20and%20was%20able%20to%20get%20a%20small%20promotion%20that%20generated%20a%20raise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20get%20paid%20more%20at%20your%20full-time%20job%2C%20consider%20one%20of%20these%20side%20hustles%20that%20can%20help%20you%20nurture%20or%20develop%20new%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22470c6096-8be2-4bf8-8859-61d75ea3be6e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Freelancing%20your%20current%20skills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20side%20hustles%20I%20ever%20started%20was%20easy%20to%20do.%20I%20was%20working%20full-time%20as%20a%20copywriter%20and%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20freelance%20writer%20in%20hopes%20of%20being%20able%20to%20work%20on%20different%20types%20of%20projects%20and%20broaden%20the%20scope%20of%20what%20I%20was%20capable%20of%20working%20on%20as%20a%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20job%2C%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20writing%20scripts%20for%20video%20ads%2C%20but%20through%20freelance%20work%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20work%20on%20blog%20posts%20for%20B2B%20companies%2C%20social%20media%20content%2C%20and%20website%20copy.%20All%20of%20this%20allowed%20me%20to%20improve%20as%20a%20writer%20and%20show%20my%20boss%20a%20portfolio%20of%20updated%20work%2C%20which%20allowed%20me%20to%20take%20on%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20the%20company%20as%20a%20copywriter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you%20determine%20a%20skill%20or%20two%20that%20you're%20currently%20doing%20well%20but%20want%20to%20expand%2C%20create%20a%20profile%20on%20a%20freelancing%20website%20like%20%3Cspan%3EFiverr%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.upwork.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUpwork%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.toptal.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EToptal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20offer%20your%20services%20to%20other%20brands%20or%20companies%20that%20need%20temporary%20help.%20Before%20you%20take%20this%20step%2C%20check%20your%20employment%20agreement%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20can%20do%20freelance%20work%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20taken%20o