%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20arrangement%20with%20Panama%2C%20a%20first%20since%201999%2C%20will%20effectively%20end%20China's%20influence%20in%20the%20Panama%20Canal%2C%20he%20suggested.%20%26quot%3BChina%20did%20not%20build%20this%20canal.%20China%20does%20not%20operate%20this%20canal%20and%20China%20will%20not%20weaponize%20this%20canal.%20Together%20with%20Panama%20in%20the%20lead%2C%20we%20will%20keep%20the%20canal%20secure%20and%20available%20for%20all%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20chief%20also%20praised%20President%20Mulino%2C%20saying%20his%20government%20understood%20%26quot%3Bthe%20threat%20from%20China%26quot%3B.%20His%20remarks%20about%20Panama%20being%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Blead%26quot%3B%20on%20addressing%20the%20canal's%20security%20concerns%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20nod%20to%20Panamanian%20sensitivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Secretary%20Hegseth%20spoke%20about%20removing%20Chinese%20influence%20from%20Panama%2C%20President%20Trump%20has%20spoken%20in%20broader%20terms%20and%20not%20ruled%20out%20using%20military%20force%2C%20if%20necessary.%20Even%20before%20Mr%20Hegseth%20reached%20Panama%2C%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20had%20reportedly%20requested%20options%20from%20the%20US%20military%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20had%20built%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20more%20than%20a%20century%20ago%20and%20handed%20its%20complete%20operations%20over%20to%20Panama%20in%201999.%20Today's%20development%20changes%20that%20dynamic%20with%20the%20US%20military%20likely%20to%20start%20patrolling%20and%20accessing%20the%20canal%20frequently%2C%20and%20in%20coordination%20with%20Panama's%20security%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20Reuters%2C%20several%20current%20and%20former%20US%20officials%20and%20strategic%20experts%20say%20that%20the%20United%20States%20has%20found%20a%20willing%20partner%20in%20tackling%20Chinese%20influence%20in%20Panamanian%20President%20Jose%20Raul%20Mulino.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20President%20Mulino%20had%20announced%20Panama's%20formal%20move%20to%20exit%20China's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%20He%20has%20also%20aided%20Donald%20Trump's%20crackdown%20on%20migrants%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20He%20did%20so%20by%20accepting%20US'%20deportation%20flights%20of%20non-Panamanians%20and%20worked%20to%20curb%20migration%20from%20South%20America%20by%20those%20crossing%20illegally%20through%20his%20country's%20dangerous%20Darien%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20move%20last%20month%2C%20US%20firm%20BlackRock%20led%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20out%20most%20of%20the%20%2422.8-billion%20ports%20business%20of%20Hong%20Kong%20conglomerate%20CK%20Hutchison%2C%20including%20its%20ports%20on%20either%20end%20of%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%20At%20the%20time%20President%20Trump%20celebrated%20the%20deal%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20purchase%20was%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%26quot%3Breclaiming%20the%20Panama%20Canal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20however%2C%20had%20slammed%20the%20deal.%20The%20markets%20regulator%20has%20said%20that%20it%20will%20carry%20out%20an%20antitrust%20review%20of%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitary%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20war%20in%20Asia%2C%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20as%20US%20naval%20ships%20cross%20from%20the%20Atlantic%20to%20the%20Pacific%20to%20support%20war%20efforts.%20With%20China's%20vast%20presence%20in%20and%20around%20the%20canal%2C%20it%20could%20hinder%20the%20passage%20of%20ships%2C%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20if%20Beijing%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20stop%20American%20naval%20vessels%20in%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20it%20would%20be%20in%20an%20advantageous%20position%20by%20being%20able%20to%20surveil%20vessels%20passing%20through%20it.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0