24032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Super%20Nintendo%20World%20at%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f43c133fe8d39283625fec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20never%20experienced%20a%20theme%20park%20like%20this%20in%20my%20life.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20almost%20sensory%20overload%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20chomping%20Piranha%20Plants%20and%20question%20mark%20blocks%20everywhere%2C%20and%20towering%20palm%20trees%20in%20the%20Donkey%20Kong%20Country%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20less%20time%20in%20the%20remaining%20three%20worlds%2C%20but%20it%20was%20enough%20to%20leave%20an%20impression.%20The%20Wizarding%20World%20of%20Harry%20Potter%20-%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20was%20also%20incredibly%20immersive%2C%20with%20shops%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20street%20performers%20that%20bring%20the%20magical%20version%20of%201920s%20Paris%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BFantastic%20Beasts%20and%20Where%20to%20Find%20Them%26quot%3B%20franchise%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20lover%20of%20all%20things%20spooky%2C%20Dark%20Universe%20was%20another%20highlight.%20Frankenstein's%20castle%20was%20so%20creepy%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20the%20street%20performers%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20woman%20playing%20violin%2C%20and%20the%20bandaged%20Invisible%20Man%20stalking%20through%20the%20crowd%20and%20avoiding%20selfies%20with%20excited%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelestial%20Park%20has%20an%20astrological%20motif%20and%2C%20unlike%20the%20other%20four%20worlds%2C%20it's%20not%20based%20on%20any%20pre-existing%20Universal%20intellectual%20property%20%E2%80%94%20rather%2C%20it%20just%20plays%20into%20the%20%26quot%3BUniverse%26quot%3B%20theme%2C%20serving%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhub%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20park%20that%20connects%20the%20other%20four%20worlds.%20While%20the%20least%20immersive%20of%20the%20five%20worlds%2C%20design-wise%2C%20Celestial%20Park%20had%20one%20of%20the%20best%20rides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c209afa-84c9-47db-a38b-20d2c33c3ddc%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20rides%20in%20Epic%20Universe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rode%20most%20of%20the%20attractions%20during%20the%20preview%2C%20and%20a%20few%20stood%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Stardust%20Racers%20ride%20in%20Celestial%20Park%20at%20Epic%20Universe%2C%20the%20new%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort%20theme%20park%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f43c713fe8d39283626000%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStardust%20Racers%20was%20an%20intense%20roller%20coaster.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-rides-roller-coasters-us-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20roller%20coaster%3C%2Fa%3E%20ride%20in%20Epic%20Universe%20is%20Stardust%20Racers%20in%20Celestial%20Park%2C%20an%20intense%20dueling%20coaster%20that%20reaches%20speeds%20of%2062%20miles%20per%20hour%2C%20sending%20riders%20through%20steep%20drops%2C%20loops%2C%20and%20corkscrews.%20There%20are%20two%20separate%20tracks%20that%20cross%20over%20one%20another%20during%20the%20ride.%20FYI%3A%20The%20right%20side%20when%20you%20enter%20the%20queue%20is%20the%20slightly%20more%20intense%20experience%2C%20I'm%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20single%20best%20ride%20in%20the%20park%2C%20however%2C%20is%20Monsters%20Unchained%3A%20The%20Frankenstein%20Experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Monster%20Unchained%20Frankenstein%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f444a5a466d2b74ab27abc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221167%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20monster%20(Henry)%20was%20startlingly%20lifelike.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thrilling%20dark%20ride%20takes%20you%20into%20the%20castle%20of%20Victoria%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmary-shelley-frankenstein-electricity-experiments-galvanism-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrankenstein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20Victor.%20During%20the%20course%20of%20the%20ride%2C%20you%20encounter%20all%20of%20Universal's%20classic%20movie%20monsters%2C%20including%20the%20Wolf%20Man%2C%20Dracula%2C%20Frankenstein%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Phantom%20of%20the%20Opera%20(who's%20playing%20an%20organ%20that%20shoots%20out%20flames%20when%20you%20first%20see%20him).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20animatronics%20on%20this%20ride%20are%20unreal%20and%20better%20than%20any%20I've%20ever%20seen%20in%20any%20theme%20park%20rides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20the%20preshow%2C%20visitors%20are%20treated%20to%20a%20face-to-face%20encounter%20with%20Henry%2C%20a%20massive%20eight-foot-tall%20Frankenstein's%20monster%20that%20moves%20so%20smoothly%20you'd%20easily%20mistake%20it%20for%20a%20real%2C%20albeit%20very%20tall%2C%20actor%20in%20a%20monster%20suit.%20It%20even%20takes%20a%20few%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20runner-up%20for%20best%20overall%20ride%20(by%20a%20very%20slim%20margin)%20is%20the%20Battle%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Magic.%20If%20you%20thought%20Universal%20Island%20of%20Adventure's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharry-potter-rides-universal-orlando-ranked-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarry%20Potter%20and%20the%20Forbidden%20Journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20impressive%2C%20just%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20ministry%20of%20magic%20in%20the%20queue%20for%20Battle%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20ride%20at%20Epic%20Universe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f43e86a466d2b74ab279bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20detailing%20inside%20the%20park's%20recreation%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20is%20jaw-dropping.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pre-show%20almost%20rivals%20the%20ride%20itself.%20Riders%20enter%20via%20the%20%26quot%3BMetrofloo%26quot%3B%20(powered%20by%20green%20%26quot%3Bfloo%20powder%26quot%3B%20that%20allows%20wizards%20to%20magically%20travel%20instantaneously)%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebefore%20walking%20through%20a%20massive%2C%20painstakingly%20detailed%20replica%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20from%20the%20movies.%20The%20ride%20is%20set%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Dolores%20Umbridge's%20trial%20as%20she%20breaks%20loose%2C%20assisted%20by%20Voldemort's%20Death%20Eaters%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20like%20you're%20right%20in%20the%20film%20alongside%20Harry%2C%20Ron%2C%20and%20Hermione%20as%20they%20attempt%20to%20re-capture%20Umbridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20the%20robotics%20work%20here%20is%20out%20of%20this%20world.%20The%20massive%20Death%20Eaters%20loom%20over%20riders%20as%20you%20zoom%20through%20the%20dark%20ride%2C%20and%20there%20are%20several%20moments%20where%20the%20animatronics%20and%20augmented%20reality%20are%20virtually%20seamless.%20The%20storytelling%20and%20build%20are%20on%20par%20with%20some%20of%20Disney's%20most%20advanced%20(and%20expensive)%20rides%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-disneyland-star-wars-rise-of-the-resistance-ride-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStar%20Wars%3A%20Rise%20of%20the%20Resistance%3C%2Fa%3E%20attraction%20in%20Hollywood%20Studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b7d8c92a-ad19-4082-a542-3fa051b70c9b%5C%22%3EEpic%20Universe%20is%20going%20to%20lure%20plenty%20of%20Disney%20lovers%20through%20its%20portal%2C%20and%20it's%20worth%20the%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20to%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort%20before%2C%20but%20not%20for%20many%20years.%20I've%20personally%20always%20opted%20for%20Disney%20World%20during%20my%20trips%20to%20central%20Florida%2C%20specifically%20because%20of%20how%20immersive%20it%20feels%20and%20how%20specifically%20branded%20each%20of%20the%20four%20Disney%20theme%20parks%20%E2%80%94%20Epcot%2C%20Hollywood%20Studios%2C%20Animal%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20Magic%20Kingdom%20%E2%80%94%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20existing%20three%20Universal%20parks%20in%20Orlando%20%E2%80%94%20Universal%20Studios%20Florida%2C%20Islands%20of%20Adventure%2C%20and%20the%20Volcano%20Bay%20water%20park%20%E2%80%94%20are%20great%20but%20have%20never%20quite%20hooked%20me%20the%20way%20Disney%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpic%20Universe%20accomplishes%20that%20full%20immersion%20in%20a%20way%20I%20haven't%20experienced%20at%20Universal%20Orlando%20before.%20It's%20clear%20the%20company%20has%20leveled%20up%20with%20its%20massive%20investment%20in%20the%20park%2C%20which%20is%20the%20first%20completely%20new%20theme%20park%20built%20in%20Orlando%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Epic%20Universe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f44707c6ad288d147d787c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEpic%20Universe%20is%20also%20just%20super%20pretty.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20has%20also%20increasingly%20become%20known%20for%20its%20dining%20options%20%E2%80%94%20many%20epicures%20make%20an%20annual%20pilgrimage%20just%20for%20Epcot's%20Food%20and%20Wine%20Festival%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Epic%20Universe's%20food%20scene%20may%20rival%20that%20aspect%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20were%20too%20busy%20taking%20in%20the%20five%20%26quot%3Bworlds%26quot%3B%20to%20sample%20many%20of%20the%20park's%20food%20and%20beverage%20offerings%2C%20theme%20park%20reporter%20Carly%20Caramanna%20attended%20an%20early%20preview%20and%20previously%20wrote%20for%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-epic-universe-theme-park-food-first-look-photos-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEpic%20Universe's%20dining%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20a%20foodie's%20paradise.%20It%20will%20introduce%20over%20100%20menu%20items%20new%20to%20Universal's%20parks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20get%20to%20eat%20at%20the%20Oak%20and%20Star%20Tavern%20in%20the%20Celestial%20Park%20section%20of%20the%20park%2C%20and%20the%20selections%20were%20impressive.%20We%20dined%20buffet-style%20for%20the%20event%2C%20but%20the%20menu%20will%20typically%20be%20%C3%A0%20la%20carte%20during%20regular%20opening%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20solid%20barbecue%20selections%20(including%20a%20vegetarian%20BBQ%20jackfruit%20option)%20and%20some%20great%20sides%20(I'm%20still%20thinking%20about%20the%20delicious%20mango%20bread%20days%20later)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20full%20bar.%20The%20spacious%20interior%2C%20with%20its%20pretty%20%26quot%3Bcosmic%20garden%26quot%3B%20theme%2C%20even%20looks%20like%20it%20could%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-planner-shares-what-to-ask-when-choosing-venue-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20venue%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20Oak%20and%20Star%20Tavern%20at%20Celestial%20Park%20in%20Epic%20Universe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f43fa6a466d2b74ab279f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Oak%20and%20Star%20Tavern%20was%20a%20beautiful%20space%20with%20solid%20barbecue%20options.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDennis%20L.%20Speigel%2C%20the%2