n%20Hospital%2C%20Damoh.%20And%20he%20stands%20accused%20not%20only%20of%20forgery%2C%20fraud%20and%20endangering%20lives%2C%20the%20hospital%20has%20also%20accused%20him%20of%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20from%20February%202%20obtained%20by%20NDTV%20shows%20him%20arriving%20at%20the%20hospital%20accompanied%20by%20a%20personal%20bouncer%20carrying%20a%20suitcase.%20The%20suitcase%20allegedly%20contained%20a%20portable%20echo%20machine%2C%20now%20reported%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20took%20our%20portable%20echo%20machine%20worth%20Rs%205-7%20lakh.%20We%20have%20lodged%20a%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pushpa%20Khare%2C%20Manager%2C%20Mission%20Hospital.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fake%20Degrees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnNDTV%20has%20traced%20Narendra%20Yadav's%20alleged%20degrees%3A%20MBBS%20from%20North%20Bengal%20Medical%20College%2C%20MRCP%20from%20St%20George's%20Hospital%2C%20London%2C%20DM%20(Cardiology)%20from%20Pondicherry%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20credentials%20don't%20hold%20up%20under%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20MBBS%20registration%20number%20belongs%20to%20a%20female%20doctor%2C%20and%20no%20credible%20records%20exist%20for%20the%20other%20qualifications.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20degree%20appears%20to%20be%20fake%20and%20morphed%2C%26quot%3B%20confirmed%20senior%20police%20officer%20SP%20Shrutkirti%20Somvanshi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20mobile%2C%20tab%2C%20and%20even%20emails%20suggest%20fabricated%20identities.%20He%20has%20possibly%20been%20operating%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20impersonating%20a%20doctor%20for%20seven%20or%20eight%20years.%20We%20are%20questioning%20him%20using%20medical%20terminology%20to%20verify%20the%20extent%20of%20his%20knowledge-or%20lack%20thereof%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E19%20Years%20Ago%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Yadav's%20fraudulent%20practices%20came%20to%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20he%20operated%20on%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20Shukla%20at%20the%20Apollo%20hospital.%20Sources%20said%20sources%20during%20his%20tenure%2C%20eight%20patients%20died%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20too%2C%20investigations%20pointed%20toward%20a%20fake%20MBBS%20degree.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BI%20was%20present%20when%20my%20father's%20surgery%20took%20place.%20I%20grew%20suspicious%20after%20seeing%20repeated%20catheter%20removals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anil%20Shukla%2C%20retired%20High%20Court%20judge%20and%20son%20of%20the%20late%20Speaker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20Apollo%20Hospital%20branding%20him%20as%20a%20London-returned%20expert%2C%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cnwe%20were%20misled.%20This%20case%20deserves%20a%20probe%20by%20a%20sitting%20High%20Court%20judge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Chief%20Medical%20and%20Health%20Officer%20of%20Bilaspur%2C%20Dr%20Pramod%20Tiwari%2C%20has%20now%20taken%20action%20against%20Apollo%20Hospital.%20A%20formal%20notice%20has%20been%20issued%20to%20the%20hospital%20management%2C%20seeking%20a%20detailed%20explanation%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20fake%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20submit%20all%20documents%20of%20his%20educational%20qualifications%20and%20clarify%20what%20action%2C%20if%20any%2C%20was%20taken%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20deaths%20of%20several%20patients%2C%20including%20the%20former%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Congress%20delegation%20meanwhile%20visited%20Apollo%20Hospital%20and%20demanded%20details%20about%20Narendra%20Yadav's%20appointment%20and%20the%20verification%20process%20of%20his%20documents.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20his%2042-day%20tenure%20at%20the%20Damoh%20Mission%20Hospital%2C%20the%20imposter%20examined%20around%2070%20patients%20and%20conducted%2015%20surgeries%2C%20seven%20of%20which%20proved%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Medical%20and%20Health%20Officer%20or%20CMHO%20and%20the%20agency%20that%20facilitated%20his%20hiring%20will%20also%20be%20questioned%2C%20said%20Ms%20Somvanshi.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20into%20who%20is%20responsible%2C%20from%20the%20agency%20to%20hospital%20officials.%20CMHO's%20statement%20will%20also%20be%20recorded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%20highlights%20the%20systemic%20failure%20that%20extends%20from%20the%20hospital's%20verification%20process%2C%20to%20Medical%20Council's%20lack%20of%20due%20diligence%2C%20and%20the%20misplaced%20trust%20of%20families%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744131240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Filmm2os8_damoh-fake-doctor_625x300_08_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-from-madhya-pradesh-to-chhattisgarh-fake-doctor-narendra-yadavs-trail-8118886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Narendra%20Vikramaditya%20Yadav%2C%20alias%20Dr%20N%20John%20Kamm%2C%20a%20man%20who%20posed%20as%20a%20UK-returned%20cardiologist%20and%20treated%20dozens%20of%20patients%20at%20Damoh's%20Mission%20Hospital%20without%20a%20valid%20medical%20license%2C%20will%20be%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20five%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-from-madhya-pradesh-to-chhattisgarh-fake-doctor-narendra-yadavs-trail-8118886%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20administration%20ends%20legal%20stay%20for%20migrants%20who%20entered%20via%20CBP%20One%20app%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744130929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fph