mes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flaapata-ladies-writer-biplab-goswami-defends-against-plagiarism-claims-in-exclusive-interview%2Farticleshow%2F120101474.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F120101474.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBiplab%20Goswami%2C%20the%20writer%20of%20the%20critically%20acclaimed%20film%20'Laapataa%20Ladies%2C'%20has%20addressed%20plagiarism%20allegations%2C%20asserting%20the%20film's%20originality.%20Goswami%20refuted%20claims%20of%20resemblance%20to%20the%20French%20short%20film%20'Burqa%20City%2C'%20highlighting%20the%20distinct%20narrative%20and%20cinematic%20treatment%20of%20'Laapataa%20Ladies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Subhash%20K%20Jha%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flaapata-ladies-writer-biplab-goswami-defends-against-plagiarism-claims-in-exclusive-interview%2Farticleshow%2F120101474.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujaratis%20Make%20Electoral%20Debut%20In%20Canada%20As%20Punjabis%20Seek%20Re-Election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujaratis%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20bloc%2C%20even%20as%20Punjabis%20remain%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with%20in%20Canada's%20political%20sphere%2C%20as%20immigrants%20of%20Indian%20origin%20steadily%20gain%20ground%20in%20the%20North%20American%20country%20which%20will%20hold%20federal%20elections%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20diaspora%20in%20Canada%20is%20vibrant%20and%20diverse%20-%20from%20Punjabis%20and%20Gujaratis%2C%20to%20Bengalis%20and%20Malayalis.%20While%20most%20migrants%20within%20the%20Indian-Canadian%20community%20are%20either%20students%20or%20highly-skilled%20employees%2C%20Gujaratis%20and%20Punjabis%20usually%20have%20a%20business%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20Punjabis%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20who%20ventured%20into%20the%20political%20arena%2C%20but%20come%202025%2C%20Gujaratis%20are%20making%20a%20debut.%20Brampton%20in%20Ontario%20and%20Calgary%20in%20Alberta%2C%20both%20with%20a%20sizeable%20Indian-Canadian%20population%2C%20have%20emerged%20as%20battleground%20cities%20as%20four%20Gujarati-origin%20candidates%20are%20contesting%20for%20parliamentary%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPOLITICAL%20DEBUT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20Gujarati-origin%20candidates%20are%20first-generation%20immigrants.%20While%20Punjabis%20have%20a%20clear%20advantage%20in%20terms%20of%20numbers%2C%20representation%2C%20and%20a%20history%20in%20Canadian%20politics%20-%20from%20MPs%2C%20to%20ministers%2C%20some%20as%20senior%20as%20a%20Cabinet%20rank%2C%20Gujaratis%20have%20spent%20decades%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20with%20an%20enterprising%20outlook%20and%20community%20service.%20They%20have%20also%20significantly%20gained%20ground%20in%20terms%20of%20social%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20Gujarati-origin%20Indian-Canadians%20contesting%20in%20Canada's%2045th%20federal%20election%2C%20scheduled%20on%20April%2028%2C%202025%20are%20Jayesh%20Brahmbhatt%2C%20Sunjiv%20Raval%2C%20Ashok%20Patel%2C%20and%20Minesh%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKEY%20CONTESTANTS%20-%20A%20BRIEF%20HISTORY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJayesh%20Brahmbhatt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20contesting%20the%20parliamentary%20election%20from%20Brampton%20Chinguacousy%20Park%2C%20moved%20from%20India%20to%20Canada%20in%202001.%20A%20civil%20engineer%20by%20profession%2C%20Mr%20Brahmbhatt%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20successful%20real%20estate%20developer%20in%20Canada.%20Living%20in%20Canada%20for%20almost%20quarter%20of%20a%20century%20now%2C%20he%20ventured%20into%20politics%20and%20has%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%20by%20the%20People's%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Times%20of%20India%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20stand%20for%20freedom%2C%20responsibility%2C%20fairness%20and%20respect%20for%20all%2C%20and%20somewhere%20it%20resonates%20with%20me%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20is%20confident%20of%20a%20win%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20spoken%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20and%20they%20seek%20change%20from%20this%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20and%20regional%20sub-communities%20in%20Canada%2C%20Mr%20Brahmbhatt%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPolitical%20parties%20in%20Canada%20are%20now%20identifying%20Indians%20as%20an%20important%20community%20in%20the%20political%20arena%2C%20and%20sub-groups%20such%20as%20Gujaratis%20are%20making%20the%20most%20of%20this%20opportunity%20to%20be%20represented%20and%20be%20heard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESunjiv%20Raval%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20another%20Gujarati-origin%20Indian-Canadian%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20parliamentary%20election%20from%20Calgary%20Midnapore.%20He%20has%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%20by%20the%20Liberal%20Party%20of%20Canada.%20Mr%20Raval%20is%20a%20successful%20businessman%20who%20owns%20a%20chain%20of%20stores.%20Since%20moving%20to%20Calgary%20more%20than%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20community%20work%20and%20has%20represented%20several%20Indian%20community%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20issue%20much%20talked%20about%20by%20Canadians%2C%20Mr%20Raval%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20fighting%20on%20issues%20faced%20by%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20better%20infrastructure%20and%20sports%20facilities%2C%20affordable%20housing%20and%20work%20opportunities%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20the%20other%20political%20issue%20-%20immigration%20-%20requires%20a%20balanced%20approach.%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20needs%20immigrants%2C%20but%20there%20must%20be%20a%20balance.%20We%20hope%20to%20restore%20it%20with%20the%20right%20policies.%20We%20have%20a%20voice%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20person%20of%20Gujarati%20descent%20contesting%20the%20Canadian%20election%20this%20month%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EAshok%20Patel%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20He%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EMinesh%20Patel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20fourth%20Gujarati%20entering%20Canadian%20politics%2C%20are%20contesting%20as%20Independent%20candidates.%20While%20Ashok%20Patel%20is%20contesting%20from%20Edmonton%20Sherwood%2C%20Minesh%20Patel%20has%20filed%20his%20nomination%20papers%20from%20Calgary%20Skyview.%20Both%20are%20from%20a%20business%20background%20and%20are%20now%20looking%20to%20serve%20fellow%20Canadians%20by%20becoming%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservative%20Party%20of%20Canada%20had%20picked%20a%20fifth%20Gujarati%20as%20one%20of%20their%20candidates%20briefly.%20His%20name%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EDon%20Patel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20successful%20realtor%20from%20Gujarat's%20Anand.%20He%20was%20considered%20for%20a%20ticket%20from%20Etobicoke%20North%2C%20but%20didn%3Bt%20make%20the%20final%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'NOT%20A%20SURPRISE'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20a%20massive%20shift%20in%20Indian%20community%20representation%20in%20Canada.%20From%20being%20dominated%20by%20Punjabis%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20Gujaratis%20in%20Canada's%20political%20landscape%20has%20led%20to%20diversity%20in%20representation%2C%20thereby%20giving%20the%20Canadian%20voters%20a%20greater%20choice.%20Gujaratis%20are%20not%20replacing%20or%20competing%20with%20Punjabis%2C%20but%20are%20adding%20to%20the%20Indian%20community's%20political%20base.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20welcome%20move%20as%20culturally%20diverse%20values%20will%20now%20shape%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fnri%2Fus-canada-news%2Fgujaratis-step-into-space-long-shaped-by-punjabis-in-canadian-politics%2Farticleshow%2F120074073.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20Gujaratis%20in%20Canada's%20politics%2C%20Hemant%20Shah%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20International%20Trade%20at%20Overseas%20Friends%20of%20India%20Canada%20(OFIC)%2C%20said%20he%20saw%20this%20coming.%20It%20isn't%20a%20surprise%2C%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BCanada%20is%20home%20to%20more%20than%201%20lakh%20Gujaratis.%20The%20community%20is%20present%20in%20almost%20all%20major%20cities%2C%20but%20more%20so%20in%20Toronto%2C%20Montreal%2C%20Ottawa%2C%20Calgary%20and%20Vancouver.%20Many%20came%20to%20the%20country%20as%20immigrants%20whereas%20many%20more%20arrived%20as%20students%20and%20settled%20here.%20I%20have%20been%20in%20Canada%20for%20over%20four%20decades%20now%2C%20and%20in%20this%20election%2C%20we%20are%20perhaps%20witnessing%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20candidates%20of%20Gujarati%20origin.%20Irrespective%20of%20their%20win%2C%20it%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20in%20ensuring%20representation%20of%20the%20community%2C%20which%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20after%20Punjabis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20KNOWN%20TURF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjabi%20representation%20in%20Canadian%20politics%20has%20been%20known%20for%20a%20while%20now.%20Some%20of%20prominent%20names%20include%20Jagmeet%20Singh%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20New%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20the%20first%20Sikh%20leader%20to%20head%20a%20party%20in%20Canada%3B%20Anita%20Anand%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20Minister%20of%20Innovation%2C%20Science%2C%20and%20Industry%3B%20Kamal%20Khera%2C%20the%20current%20Minister%20of%20Health%3B%20Sukh%20Dhaliwal%2C%20a%20Liberal%20Party%20MP%2C%20and%20Bardish%20Chagger%2C%20the%20former%20minister%20of%20diversity%2C%20inclusion%2C%20and%20youth.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744129920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F18h0fg44_canada-parliament-reuters_625x300_24_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgujaratis-make-electoral-debut-in-canada-as-punjabis-seek-re-election-8118732%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujaratis%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20bloc%2C%20even%20as%20Punjabis%20remain%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with%20in%20Canada's%20political%20sphere%2C%20as%20immigrants%20of%20Indian%20origin%20steadily%20gain%20ground%20in%20the%20North%20American%20country%20which%20will%20hold%20federal%20elections%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgujaratis-make-electoral-debut-in-canada-as-punjabis-seek-re-election-8118732%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20growth%20trajectory%20remains%20strong%2C%20says%20FM%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744129422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-growth-trajectory-remains-strong-says-fm-nirmala-sitharaman-125040801363_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOur%20government%20remains%20committed%20to%20continued%20reforms%2C%20maintaining%20macroeconomic%20stability%2C%20and%20ensuring%20that%20growth%20benefits%20every%20section%20of%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World's%20'exceptional'%20heat%20streak%20lengthens%20into%20March%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744128974000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120101060%2Cimgsize-18456.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fworlds-exceptional-heat-streak-lengthens-into-march%2Farticleshow%2F120101061.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F120101061.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGlobal%20temperatures%20soared%20to%20historic%20highs%20in%20March%2C%20continuing%20an%20unprecedented%20heat%20streak%20that%20challenges%20scientific%20understanding.%20Europe%20experienced%20its%20hottest%20March%20ever%2C%20leading%20to%20extreme%20rainfall%20variations.%20The%20world%20marked%20its%20second-hottest%20March%2C%20sustaining%20record-breaking%20temperatures%20since%20July%202023%2C%20with%20scientists%20noting%20the%20persistent%20anomaly%20and%20its%20link%20to%20human-caused%20climate%20change.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fworlds-exceptional-heat-streak-lengthens-into-march%2Farticleshow%2F120101061.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fworlds-exceptional-heat-streak-lengthens-into-march%2Famp_articleshow%2F120101061.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fworlds-exceptional-heat-streak-lengthens-into-march%2Famp_articleshow%2F120101061.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20US%20Is%20Revoking%20Student%20Visas%20Overnight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInternational%20students%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20facing%20a%20myriad%20of%20challenges%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20the%20revocation%20of%20their%20student%20visas.%20The%20F-1%20visa%2C%20which%20allows%20foreign%20students%20to%20study%20full-time%20at%20certified%20schools%20under%20the%20Student%20and%20Exchange%20Visitor%20Program%20(SEVP)%2C%20comes%20with%20a%20set%20of%20strict%20conditions%20that%20must%20be%20met%20to%20maintain%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcademic-Related%20Risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Dropping%20below%20the%20required%20course%20load%20can%20lead%20to%20visa%20revocation%2C%20except%20in%20cases%20approved%20by%20Designated%20School%20Official%20(DSO).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20Dismissal%20for%20poor%20academic%20performance%20or%20disciplinary%20reasons%20can%20result%20in%20visa%20revocation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Changes%20in%20course%20format%20such%20as%20part-time%2C%20hybrid%20or%20online%20can%20affect%20visa%20status%20if%20not%20reported%20to%20SEVIS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmployment-Related%20Risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Working%20without%20proper%20CPT%20(Curricular%20Practical%20Training)%20or%20OPT%20(Optional%20Practical%20Training)%20approval%20can%20lead%20to%20visa%20revocation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20Working%20or%20interning%20at%20sanctioned%20organisations%2C%20especially%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20research%2C%20defense%2C%20or%20foreign%20funding%2C%20can%20affect%20visa%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersonal%20and%20Financial%20Risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Failure%20to%20demonstrate%20financial%20capability%20to%20fund%20education%20can%20lead%20to%20visa%20revocation.%20Just%20showing%20the%20initial%20proof%20is%20not%20enough.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20Submitting%20forged%20documents%20such%20as%20admission%20letters%2C%20test%20scores%2C%20financial%20documents%20or%20manipulated%20information%20can%20result%20in%20visa%20revocation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Not%20updating%20residential%20or%20mailing%20details%20in%20SEVIS%20can%20lead%20to%20non-compliance.%20Students%20must%20report%20any%20change%20in%20address%20within%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmigration%20and%20Security%20Risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Overstaying%20authorised%20stay%20can%20lead%20to%20bars%20from%20future%20visa%20eligibility%2C%20even%20if%20it%20happens%20by%20mistake.%20As%20mentioned%20on%20Form%20I-94%20students%20must%20leave%20the%20US%20once%20their%20authorised%20stay%20ends.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20Arrests%2C%20pending%20charges%2C%20or%20convictions%20can%20trigger%20visa%20revocation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Identification%20as%20a%20risk%20by%20US%20security%20or%20intelligence%20agencies%20can%20result%20in%20immediate%20visa%20revocation%2C%20even%20before%20court%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDependent%20and%20Transfer%20Risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Violations%20by%20dependents%20(F-2%20visa%20holders)%20can%20affect%20the%20principal%20F-1%20visa%20holder's%20status.%20If%20the%20dependents%20work%20or%20enroll%20full-time%20in%20a%20school%20without%20authorisation%2C%20the%20principal%20F-1%20visa%20holder's%20status%20can%20be%20revoked.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20If%20a%20student%20changes%20levels%20or%20schools%2C%20they%20must%20initiate%20a%20SEVIS%20transfer.%20Not%20doing%20so%2C%20within%2060%20days%20can%20lead%20to%20status%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20immigration%20agenda%20has%20introduced%20several%20new%20threats%20to%20international%20students%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20maintain%20their%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisa%20revocations%20for%20trivial%20violations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20concerning%20developments%20is%20the%20revocation%20of%20visas%20for%20minor%20infractions%2C%20such%20as%20traffic%20violations.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20these%20infractions%20occurred%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20students%20were%20not%20provided%20prior%20notice%20before%20revocation.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20student%20might%20have%20their%20visa%20revoked%20due%20to%20a%20speeding%20ticket%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20deportation%20and%20significant%20disruptions%20to%20their%20academic%20and%20career%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETargeting%20activism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20also%20been%20targeting%20students%20involved%20in%20pro-Palestinian%20activism%2C%20citing%20potential%20adverse%20foreign%20policy%20consequences.%20A%20notable%20example%20is%20R%C3%BCmeysa%20%C3%96zt%C3%BCrk%2C%20a%20Turkish%20graduate%20student%20at%20Tufts%20University%2C%20who%20was%20detained%20and%20faced%20deportation%20after%20her%20visa%20was%20annulled%20due%20to%20alleged%20support%20for%20Hamas%20through%20pro-Palestinian%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonitoring%20social%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20are%20reportedly%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20programs%20to%20monitor%20social%20media%20for%20content%20deemed%20supportive%20of%20organisations%20like%20Hamas%2C%20leading%20to%20visa%20revocations.%20This%20approach%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20privacy%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20misinterpretation%20of%20online%20activity.%20The%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20(DHS)%20has%20legal%20authority%20to%20review%20students'%20online%20profiles%20and%20posts%2C%20and%20content%20that%20appears%20political%2C%20anti-US%2C%20or%20linked%20to%20prohibited%20groups%20may%20raise%20red%20flags%20during%20visa%20processing%20or%20renewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECountry-specific%20policies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20implemented%20country-specific%20visa%20policies%2C%20revoking%20visas%20based%20on%20nationality.%20For%20example%2C%20South%20Sudanese%20students%2C%20including%20Duke%20University%20basketball%20star%20Khaman%20Maluach%2C%20faced%20deportation%20under%20a%20new%20directive%20revoking%20visas%20held%20by%20South%20Sudanese%20passport%20holders%20due%20to%20their%20country's%20failure%20to%20accept%20repatriated%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20executive%20order%20to%20end%20birthright%20citizenship%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20executive%20order%20aims%20to%20end%20birthright%20citizenship%20for%20children%20born%20to%20individuals%20on%20temporary%20visas.%20This%20affects%20students%20who%20become%20parents%20in%20the%20U.S.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELack%20of%20notification%20and%20transparency%20to%20educational%20institutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColleges%20and%20universities%20are%20not%20informed%20when%20their%20students'%20visas%20are%20revoked%2C%20leaving%20institutions%20unable%20to%20provide%20support%20or%20guidance%20in%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsequences%20of%20increased%20institutional%20scrutiny%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20(DHS)%20and%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20have%20increased%20audits%20of%20school%20records%20and%20SEVIS%20data.%20Inconsistencies%20the%20records%20can%20lead%20to%20visa%20violations%20or%20school%20penalties.%20The%20administration%20also%20plans%20to%20review%20institutions%20with%20significant%20pro-Palestinian%20protests%2C%20indicating%20that%20such%20schools%20could%20lose%20certification%20to%20enroll%20student%20visa%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUncertainty%20of%20visa%20revocation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20visa%20can%20be%20canceled%20at%20any%20time%20by%20a%20consulate%20or%20border%20officer%20if%20the%20government%20receives%20information%20about%20the%20student%20being%20ineligible.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744128960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-01%2Fstatue-of-liberty_650x400_61516584069.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsurprising-reasons-why-us-is-revoking-student-visas-overnight-8118491%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20F-1%20visa%2C%20which%20allows%20foreign%20students%20to%20study%20full-time%20at%20certified%20schools%20under%20the%20Student%20and%20Exchange%20Visitor%20Program%2