22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress%20Going%20To%20Have%20Massive%20Organisational%20Reshuffle%26quot%3B%3A%20Senior%20Leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20going%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20organisational%20reshuffle%26quot%3B%2C%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20the%20party's%20top%20leaders%20met%20in%20Ahmedabad%20and%20vowed%20to%20embark%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bpath%20of%20social%20justice%26quot%3B%20espoused%20by%20Sardar%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBriefing%20reporters%20after%20the%20extended%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20meeting%20at%20the%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20National%20Memorial%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Mr%20Venugopal%20noted%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20dedicated%20this%20year%20to%20a%20complete%20restructuring%20of%20the%20party%20organisation%20and%20the%20issue%20was%20discussed%20at%20length%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20have%20a%20massive%20organisational%20reshuffle%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20guidelines%20for%20the%20same.%20Our%20general%20secretaries%20and%20in-charges%20are%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Venugopal%20also%20stressed%20that%20measures%20to%20empower%20the%20party's%20district%20unit%20chiefs%20will%20be%20rolled%20out%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20decided%20on%20that%20issue%2C%20empowering%20the%20DCC%20presidents%20and%20duties%20and%20powers%20of%20the%20DCCs%20has%20been%20discussed%20in%20various%20forums%2C%20already%20general%20secretaries%20and%20in-charges%20have%20approved%20the%20proposals%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20roll%20out%20that%20proposal%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20replying%20to%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Venugopal%20said%20the%20Extended%20CWC%20passed%20a%20resolution%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20party%20will%20walk%20on%20the%20path%20showed%20to%20us%20by%20Sardar%20Patel%20ji%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20stood%20up%20against%20the%20oppression%20of%20the%20British%2C%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20workers%20and%20farmers.%20He%20rejected%20communal%20forces%20after%20Bapu's%20assassination.%20He%20fought%20for%20an%20India%20where%20everyone%20had%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20freedoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20as%20we%20embark%20on%20the%20path%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20our%20Nyay%20Path%20follows%20the%20same%20principles%20laid%20down%20by%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opening%20address%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20also%20asserted%20the%20party's%20claim%20to%20Sardar%20Patel's%20legacy%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20of%20trying%20to%20usurp%20it%20under%20a%20%26quot%3Bwell-planned%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20against%20national%20heroes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20stressed%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20taking%20forward%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSardar%20Patel%20Saheb%20lives%20in%20our%20hearts%2C%20lives%20in%20our%20thoughts.%20We%20are%20taking%20his%20legacy%20forward.%20We%20have%20organised%20this%20CWC%20meeting%20in%20Ahmedabad%20at%20Sardar%20Patel%20Museum%20with%20this%20thought%20in%20mind.%20We%20pay%20our%20heartfelt%20tributes%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20Sachin%20Pilot%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20Congress%20intends%20to%20create%20more%20empowered%20district%20units%20with%20their%20presidents%20having%20enhanced%20accountability%2C%20responsibility%20and%20political%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20fight%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20with%20strength%20and%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20supporting%20ideologies%20would%20come%20together%20to%20give%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20NDA%20a%20tough%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBriefing%20reporters%20outside%20the%20venue%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20intention%20of%20the%20Congress%20president%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20is%20to%20create%20a%20more%20empowered%20district%20unit.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20accountability%2C%20the%20responsibility%20and%20the%20political%20strength%20that%20we%20have%20thus%20given%20to%20the%20district%20presidents%20is%20set%20to%20be%20enhanced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20outcome%20will%20be%20decided%20after%20the%20convention%20on%20Wednesday%20but%20the%20intention%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20to%20make%20the%20District%20Pradesh%20Congress%20(DCC)%20presidents%20more%20empowered%20than%20before%2C%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20expanding%20the%20party's%20reach%20in%20villages%2C%20divisions%20and%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20year%202025%20is%20the%20year%20of%20the%20organisation%20to%20strengthen%20our%20workers%2C%20expand%20our%20party%20ideology%20and%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20Congress%20reaches%20out%20in%20a%20mass%20contact%20programme%20through%20padyatras%20and%20door-to-door%20programmes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20wants%20to%20send%20a%20clear%20message%20not%20just%20to%20its%20opponents%20but%20to%20its%20supporters%20and%20workers%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20not%20step%20back%20and%20fight%20aggressively%20both%20within%20Parliament%20and%20outside%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20it%20wins%20the%20next%20political%20challenge%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20are%20fought%20to%20be%20won%2C%20the%20next%20few%20elections%20we%20will%20fight%20with%20strength%20and%20I%20am%20supremely%20confident%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20supporting%20ideologies%20will%20come%20together%20to%20give%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20NDA%20a%20tough%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pilot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20resolution%20passed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20session%20on%20April%209%20will%20be%20named%20'Nyay%20Path'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTomorrow'%20session%20will%20write%20a%20new%20chapter%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20The%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20announced%20that%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Session%20will%20be%20themed%20%26quot%3BNyaypath%3A%20Sankalp%2C%20Samarpan%20aur%20Sangharsh%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20more%20than%201%2C700%20elected%20and%20co-opted%20AICC%20members%20attending%20the%20main%20conclave%20on%20April%209%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Sabarmati%20river%20between%20the%20Sabarmati%20Ashram%20and%20Kochrab%20Ashram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744122360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F8njmb37o_congress_625x300_08_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-going-to-have-massive-organisational-reshuffle-senior-leader-kc-venugopal-8117177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20is%20going%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20organisational%20reshuffle%26quot%3B%2C%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20the%20party's%20top%20leaders%20met%20here%20and%20vowed%20to%20embark%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bpath%20of%20social%20justice%26quot%3B%20espoused%20by%20Sardar%20Patel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-going-to-have-massive-organisational-reshuffle-senior-leader-kc-venugopal-8117177%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20targets%2010%25%20market%20share%20in%2