0Mr%20Banerjee%2C%20he%20had%20been%20told%2027%20MPs%20(but%20not%20who)%20would%20sign%20and%20deliver%20the%20memorandum.%20%26quot%3BNext%20morning%2C%20as%20I%20reached%20the%20EC%20office%2C%20a%20female%20MP%20questioned%20me%20because%20her%20name%20was%20not%20on%20the%20list.%20She%20shouted...%20that%20her%20name%20had%20been%20deliberately%20removed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20stressed%20he%20had%20not%20been%20told%20about%20who%20will%2C%20or%20will%20not%2C%20be%20in%20the%20delegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20shouted%20and%20I%20responded...%20Then%20she%20ran%20to%20the%20BSF%20(Border%20Security%20Force)%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20arrest%20me!%20I%20have%20been%20in%20politics%20for%2040%20years...%20fought%20against%20CPM%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20BJP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20me...%20but%20this%20lady%20has%20no%20issue%20except%20with%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi...%20she%20never%20challenges%20any%20other%20BJP%20leader%2C%20even%20from%20Bengal.%20How%20dare%20she%20ask%20for%20my%20arrest%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Banerjee)%20says%20I%20am%20wrong%2C%20I%20shall%20quit%20politics%20forever.%20But%20I%20will%20not%20tolerate%20that%20rude%20female%20MP%20who%20pressures%20me%20to%20give%20her%20more%20time%20(to%20speak%20in%20Parliament).%20What%20is%20this%3F%20I%20can%20take%20pressure%20from%20anyone%20but%20I%20cannot%20take%20from%20that%20MP...%20for%20saying%20I%20have%20to%20allot%20her%20more%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20female%20MP%20-%20who%20has%20been%20backed%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20by%20Mr%20Azad%20-%20has%20not%20responded%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20end%20of%20that%20row%20was%20captured%20(secretly%2C%20it%20appears)%20on%20mobile%20phone%20footage%20and%20later%20shared%20online%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Amit%20Malviya.%20In%20that%20video%20an%20irate%20Mr%2