ever%2C%20has%20filed%20a%20caveat%20in%20the%20top%20court%2C%20in%20which%20it%20said%20no%20orders%20should%20be%20passed%20without%20hearing%20its%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%2015%20petitions%20have%20been%20filed%20on%20the%20contentious%20bill%20to%20which%20the%20Opposition%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20had%20expressed%20multiple%20objections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20were%20expressed%20during%20the%20marathon%2012-plus%20hour%20debate%20on%20the%20bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday%20last%20week.%20The%20bill%20has%20since%20been%20signed%20by%20the%20President%20and%20has%20come%20into%20force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20provisions%20in%20the%20amended%20law%20include%20mandatory%20inclusion%20of%20two%20non-Muslim%20members%20in%20the%20Central%20Waqf%20Council%20and%20Waqf%20Boards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20stipulation%20that%20individuals%20who%20practiced%20Islam%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20only%20can%20donate%20properties%20to%20Waqf.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20under%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20government%20property%20identified%20as%20Waqf%20will%20cease%20to%20belong%20to%20it%20and%20the%20local%20Collector%20will%20determine%20its%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20repeatedly%20underscored%20that%20the%20law%20is%20about%20property%20and%20its%20management%2C%20not%20religion.%20The%20Waqf%20bill%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20declared%2C%20was%20developed%20after%20consulting%20a%20large%20section%20of%20people%20and%20it%20has%20received%20the%20support%20of%20non-Muslim%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20it%20insisted%2C%20is%20because%20of%20the%20largescale%20irregularities%20that%20did%20not%20allow%20Waqf%20property%20to%20benefit%20women%20and%20children%2C%20which%20the%20amended%20law%20would%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20huge%20lands%20and%20prop