ymnastics).%20I%20was%20intrigued%20by%20the%20different%20movements%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shraddha%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%2014%20at%20the%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20natural%20step%20was%20to%20learn%20the%20art.%20But%20Shraddha%20did%20not%20have%20a%20coach%20to%20train%20her%2C%20nor%20could%20she%20afford%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20teenager%20and%20did%20not%20have%20the%20family%20support%20to%20ask%20for%20financial%20help.%20It%20forced%20me%20to%20find%20other%20ways%20to%20learn%20the%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20go%20for%20%3Cem%3EKanjak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(young%20girls%20are%20worshipped%20as%20representations%20of%20the%20Goddess)%20during%20Navratri%2C%20earn%20Rs%20100%2C%20and%20save%20it%20for%20registrations%20and%20tournaments%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESocial%20media%20to%20the%20rescue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShraddha%20quickly%20realised%20that%20pocket%20money%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20her%20long-term%20goals.%20She%20needed%20substantial%20funds%20for%20tournament%20registrations%20and%20personal%20expenses.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202020%2C%20I%20started%20to%20post%20videos%20of%20my%20training%20on%20social%20media%2C%20not%20just%20to%20showcase%20my%20skills%20but%20to%20build%20a%20platform%20for%20people%20who%20do%20not%20have%20the%20financial%20backing%20to%20learn%20tricking%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-art