uations%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Seth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20efficient%20electric%20motors%20that%20powered%20the%20looms%20turned%20futile%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20power%20cut.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291338%2Fbengaluru-couple-repurposes-old-home-to-build-eco-friendly-new-home-destination-designs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolar%20power%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20a%20great%20antidote.%20The%20women%20aren%E2%80%99t%20worried%20about%20the%20power%20supply%20hampering%20their%20work.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitongbam%20Sofia%20Devi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20weaving%20for%20years%20now%2C%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20solar%20power%20loom%2C%20is%20thrilled.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20solar%2C%20I%20had%20to%20stop%20my%20work%20around%20early%20evening%20because%20we%20have%20power%20cuts%20here.%20But%20now%2C%20I%20can%20keep%20going.%20I%20am%20also%20able%20to%20earn%20more%20because%20I%20weave%20more.%20Ever%20since%20solar%20came%20to%20us%2C%20we%20have%20had%20good%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20Seth%20planning%20to%20expand%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20potential%20to%20harvest%20the%20Sun%3F%20He%20smiles%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20his%20eye%20on%20solar%20microgrids%20(self-contained%20electrical%20networks%20which%20operate%20alongside%20the%20main%20grid).%20But%20their%20logistical%20requirements%20make%20them%20unconducive%20for%20a%20place%20like%20Manipur%2C%20which%20is%20filled%20with%20informal%20settlements%20and%20unorganised%20clusters.%20Here%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F240548%2Fhow-to-cut-power-electricity-bill-high-overcharge-solar-installation-cost-method-company-review-zero-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20independent%20solar%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20more%20viable