echnology%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20assessed%2C%20followed%20by%20intense%20community%20interactions%2C%20which%20gauge%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20ability%20and%20willingness%20to%20pay%20metered%20bills.%20The%20final%20step%20is%20ownership%20transfer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ensures%20that%20solar%20adoption%20is%20not%20a%20fleeting%20inclusion%2C%20but%20instead%20sustainable.%20Monthly%20tariff%20collections%20through%20a%20village%20committee%20bank%20account%20pin%20accountability%20on%20the%20locals.%20And%20the%20model%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20measured%20by%20a%20recent%20study%20that%20Gram%20Oorja%20conducted%2C%20where%2074%20percent%20of%20villagers%20felt%20proud%20about%20the%20solar%20installations%20being%20managed%20entirely%20by%20community%20members.%20They%20shared%20how%20it%20furthered%20their%20intent%20to%20help%20in%20the%20upkeep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20villages%20of%20India%2C%20this%20model%20%E2%80%94%20of%20putting%20the%20onus%20of%20solar%20adoption%20and%20upkeep%20on%20the%20locals%20%E2%80%94%20is%20tasting%20success.%20Take%20for%20instance%20the%20%E2%80%98Bolega%20Bihar%E2%80%99%20campaign%20(2020)%20that%20pushed%20household-level%20adoption%20of%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy%20solutions%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Gaya%20and%20Nalanda%2C%20and%20saw%20over%20700%20women%20leaders%20become%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20cause%2C%20joining%20in%20solar-related%20discussions.%20In%20another%20successful%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268152%2Fmaharashtra-village-manyachiwadi-solar-gram-electricity-sustainable-women-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Manyachiwadi%20village%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadvocates%20for%20a%20similar%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20set%20a%20precedent%20becoming%20the%20first%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20be%20100%20percent%20electrified%20by%20solar.%20Almost%20two%20decades%2